Class CallbackHandler<F extends ToxFriend>

  • java.lang.Object
    • im.tox.jtoxcore.callbacks.CallbackHandler<F>
  • Type Parameters:
    F - Friend type to use with the CallbackHandler instance

    public class CallbackHandler<F extends ToxFriend>
extends java.lang.Object
    Callback Handler class which contains methods to manage the callbacks for a JTox instance.
